{{Top|canon=Paralight tracker}}
The '''paralight system''' was a combination of mechanical and electro-optical subsystems built into the [[Hyperdrive/Legends|hyperdrive]] system of most [[Starship/Legends|starships]]. It was responsible for parsing commands from the ship's [[Computer/Legends|main computer]] into the appropriate format for the [[Hyperdrive motivator/Legends|hyperdrive motivator]] data feed.

